  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/cd684a3eb74094598073cebc6b3ed0f1.avif?t=1740440612\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras_big/cd684a3eb74094598073cebc6b3ed0f1.avif?t=1740440612 width=800 height=404 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move Dash Rush is a <strong>small and simple game</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's all about <strong>movement</strong>. It's up to you to find the best way to move and the best path to reach the finish line as quickly as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>grid-based terrain</strong>, you'll need as much <strong>dexterity</strong> as <strong>analysis</strong> to climb the <strong>leaderboard</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/93195636a25c99503f2285d9292988bb.poster.avif?t=1740440612\" width=550 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/93195636a25c99503f2285d9292988bb.webm?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/93195636a25c99503f2285d9292988bb.mp4?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move & Dash</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to learn, the game consists only on move and dash</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/fbe418a9359ca1dd80dafd78cc2559e7.avif?t=1740440612\" width=550 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stars</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slow down the pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6 stars</strong> are scattered throughout the level. Explore and try to collect them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/7d92fa1e7e5e95ea505d18cf43c0b950.poster.avif?t=1740440612\" width=550 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/7d92fa1e7e5e95ea505d18cf43c0b950.webm?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/7d92fa1e7e5e95ea505d18cf43c0b950.mp4?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TOP 10</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time to shine by making it into the TOP10. You'll need both dexterity and fine analysis to find and make the fastest path.  Will you be among the elite?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trophies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to complete the level within a specific time limit or meet certain conditions to unlock all the trophies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/ad2dd472117e40754c3588ae53f3e035.poster.avif?t=1740440612\" width=550 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/ad2dd472117e40754c3588ae53f3e035.webm?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/ad2dd472117e40754c3588ae53f3e035.mp4?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/cd684a3eb74094598073cebc6b3ed0f1.avif?t=1740440612\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras_big/cd684a3eb74094598073cebc6b3ed0f1.avif?t=1740440612 width=800 height=404 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move Dash Rush is a <strong>small and simple game</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's all about <strong>movement</strong>. It's up to you to find the best way to move and the best path to reach the finish line as quickly as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>grid-based terrain</strong>, you'll need as much <strong>dexterity</strong> as <strong>analysis</strong> to climb the <strong>leaderboard</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/93195636a25c99503f2285d9292988bb.poster.avif?t=1740440612\" width=550 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/93195636a25c99503f2285d9292988bb.webm?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/93195636a25c99503f2285d9292988bb.mp4?t=1740440612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move & Dash</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to learn, the game consists only on move and dash</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404110/extras/fbe418a9359ca1dd80dafd78cc2559e7.avif?t=1740440612\" width=550 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stars</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"